    <summary>The primary purpose of this study is to find out if high salt intake contributes to the severity of obstructive sleep apnoea. Our hypothesis is that reduction of salt intake in people with moderate to severe sleep apnoea will reduce the symptoms of the sleep apnoea.</summary>
